content = "Hello and welcome!<br>We are absolutely thrilled to have you join TBox,<br>where sending and receiving emails is just the beginning of your journey with us.<br><br>Your account is now active, and you can start enjoying our convenient email services right away.<br>Rest assured, we are committed to providing you with a seamless experience while also enhancing our services through data-driven insights.<br>By using our platform, you agree to our <a href='/privacy-policy' style='color: blue; text-decoration: none;'>Privacy Policy</a>, which enables us to, well… optimize and personalize your experience in ways you may not even realize.<br><br>If you ever have questions, our support team is here (though response times may vary). In the meantime, feel free to explore your inbox—after all, we already are!<br><br>Enjoy your new email account!<br><br>Best,<br>TBox Team"
